query: SELECT COUNT(*) as total, SUM(CASE WHEN (name IS NULL OR name = '' OR name = 'Unknown') AND (email IS NULL OR email = '') AND (phone IS NULL OR phone = '') AND (organization IS NULL OR organization = '') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as completely_empty, SUM(CASE WHEN (email IS NULL OR email = '') AND (phone IS NULL OR phone = '') AND (organization IS NULL OR organization = '') AND (title IS NULL OR title = '') AND (notes IS NULL OR notes = '') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as name_only FROM contacts;
